polito.sdp2017.VhdlInterface

Class VhdlInterface

  • java.lang.Object
    • polito.sdp2017.VhdlInterface.VhdlInterface
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HardwareInterface

    public class VhdlInterface
extends java.lang.Object
implements HardwareInterface
    A VhdlInterface is a description of a certain hardware block in VHDL. It is composed of three main elements: an entity name, a set of pins and, optionally a list of generic parameters.
